This debilitating illness is largely unrecognised because it cannot be seen. Relying on voluntary income, Chrisrhea Jewellery are supporting Endometriosis UK by raising funds and awareness. 

For every piece of jewellery purchased here using the following promotional code DONTTAKEITLYINGDOWN Chrisrhea Jewellery will donate 20% of all proceeds to Endometriosis UK.

Chrisrhea Jewellery are proud to be supporting Endometriosis UK (registered charity number - 1035810).
